Method/Procedure to destruct personal data
(procedures and methods to destroy personal information)
1. You may request to erase your data inside the App. Use "Delete Account"  button inside the Option page. (You must be signed in with an account.)
2. Or, by sending a "Data erasure" request by email to Owner to support.
