Processing and management of job applicants' recruitment procedures, personnel management, etc. See more detail above.
[Retention and Use Period]
The Data is kept for the time necessary to provide the service requested by the User, or stated by the purposes outlined in this document, and the User can always request that the Data Controller suspend or remove the data.
[Ways and impact of Refusing transfer]
Data transmission occurs solely through the network; disabling the network prevents data transfer. Our app offers an offline gaming service, enabling gameplay without an internet connection. However, it's essential to note that this may result in the failure of numerous functions such as account login, cloud data storage, ad display, and more, leading to an unsatisfactory gaming experience. Therefore, we do not recommend this approach.
